title: DCC Base Station
description:
A DCC command station based on Arduino Mega. This project is the additonal electronic for CAN
bus connectivity, power logic drives, switch, LED and LCD display interfaces. The PCB is an Arduino Mega layout so that it fits on top of the Mega.
